<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include ("partials/header") %>
    <title>Signup</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include ("partials/nav") %>
    <main style="padding: 3rem">
      <form action="/auth/signup" method="POST">
        <!-- 這個嵌入的ejs檔，如果是直接進入這個頁面(例如首頁點擊註冊會員或輸入URL)是不會有任何element的，要有經過route處理過重新導向這個頁面的才會有element -->
        <!-- 因為這個message.ejs裡面有判斷幾個flash是不是空字串，是的話就不會有任何element，而幾個flash的key所對應的值是在其他route裡才會賦予的 -->
        <%- include ("partials/message") %>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleUsername">姓名：</label>
          <input
            name="name"
            type="text"
            class="form-control"
            id="exampleUsername"
            required
            minlength="3"
            maxlength="255"
          />
          <small class="form-text text-muted">請輸入您的全名。</small>
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputEmail1">信箱地址：</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            class="form-control"
            id="exampleInputEmail1"
            aria-describedby="emailHelp"
            name="email"
            required
          />
          <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted"
            >我們不會與其他人分享你的信箱。</small
          >
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="exampleInputPassword1">密碼：</label>
          <input
            type="password"
            class="form-control"
            id="exampleInputPassword1"
            maxlength="1024"
            minlength="8"
            name="password"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <br />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">註冊用戶</button>
      </form>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
